考下，各有各做<br />\n每星期任務：1. 低消費、高儲蓄、罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手<br />\n每月任務：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=577653a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=011b8bb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=2f29fa16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@Template@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.24"},{"pid":"789618245e0f1a8e3e2383f4db6c12cccc5afb57","tid":1590224,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d0d8286e9de3ee73721dafe4692eea49354dca","tid":1590224,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d70cf047f4d87e631f2df535535d854a19b223","tid":1590224,"uid":265459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"啱,聽完再自己諗吓"},{"pid":"e8e43cc8742b13a091f48622a46a1e272521c0c9","tid":1590224,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><